ed="T" n="0859b27"/><persName key="A010735">釋<anchor xml:id="begd1e41225"/>慧<anchor xml:id="endd1e41225"/>明</persName>，俗姓蔣，<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>人也。研覈三學，漸入<lb
ed="T" n="0859b28"/>精微。後登<placeName key="PL000000017104">閩越</placeName>，殆至<placeName key="PL000000019846">臨川</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz19"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz19"/><persName key="A000174">文益禪師</persName>，深<lb
ed="T" n="0859b29"/>符正理，悟先所宗不免生滅情見。後迴<placeName key="PL000000008355">浙</placeName>，<pb ed="T" n="0859c" xml:id="T50.2061.0859c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0859c01"/>隱天台<placeName key="PL000000014398">白沙</placeName>，立草寮，有<persName key="A003677">雪峯</persName><persName key="A003890">長慶</persName>之風，到<lb
ed="T" n="0859c02"/>者皆崩角摧鋒，謂<persName key="A010735">明</persName>為魔說。漢<date key="j20673842068464" notAfter-iso="+0951-02-28" notBefore-iso="+0948-03-15">乾祐中</date>自<lb
ed="T" n="0859c03"/>山出，時<persName key="A013517">翠巖參公</persName>率諸禪伯於僧主思憲<lb
ed="T" n="0859c04"/>院<!--找不到此地-->，定其臧否。<persName key="A010735">明</persName>之口給，無能挫衂。尋漢南國<lb
ed="T" n="0859c05"/>王錢氏造<placeName key="PL000000011432">大報恩寺</placeName>，請以住持，假號<persName key="A010735">圓通普<lb
ed="T" n="0859c06"/>照禪師</persName>。然行<persName key="A008370">玄沙</persName>正眼，非<persName key="A010735">明</persName>曷能致此？<date key="j20695592071729" notAfter-iso="+0960-02-06" notBefore-iso="+0954-02-27">顯<lb
ed="T" n="0859c07"/>德中</date>卒，時酷暑，俾欲葬之。有弟子<persName key="A013518">永安</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0859c08"/>「知<persName key="A010735">師</persName>唯<persName key="A013518">我</persName>也。」請焚之，得舍利五色，一皆圓<lb
ed="T" n="0859c09"/>淨。初<persName key="A010735">明</persName><anchor xml:id="begd1e41261"/>煉<anchor xml:id="endd1e41261"/>指為燈，於<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>供養。後相繼<lb
ed="T" n="0859c10"/>燒三指，而勤持課，脇疎袵席，時說法焉。性<lb
ed="T" n="0859c11"/>且剛直，言多忤物，是其所短也。</p>
